name: Euro 2016
description: The UEFA Euro 2016 tournament held in France with 24 teams playing 51 games total (36 group stage + 15 knockout stage games).

name: UEFA Champions League 2018/19
description: The 2018–19 UEFA Champions League season with 125 games total, won by Liverpool who defeated Tottenham 2-0 in the final.

name: World Cup 2018 Russia
description: The 2018 FIFA World Cup held in Russia with 32 teams playing 64 games total (48 group stage + 16 knockout stage games). France won the tournament.

name: UEFA Champions League 2019/20
description: The 2019–20 UEFA Champions League was interrupted by the COVID-19 pandemic in March 2020. This represents the standings after 108 games (96 group stage + 12 Round of 16 first leg games).
